data.description:
Spacious Single-Family Home in Lawton

You can take a look at this versatile single-family residence at 1122 NW Laird Ave., Lawton, OK 73507. Built in 1940, this home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1 .75 bath, and approximately 2073 sq ft, with an estimated total of 2400 sq ft of potential living space, offering flexible floor plan options for 3-5 bedrooms and multiple living spaces—total square footage to be verified by the buyer.

Currently vacant, it presents a canvas of possibilities for the discerning buyer!

Please take a look at Realtor Remarks for Inquiries and Viewing Instructions
